  "title": "Civil & Structural Engineer",
  "description": "<p><u>Responsibilities:</u></p>\n<p>- Conduct RC Structural work Co-ordination meeting.</p>\n<p>- Attend site meeting &amp; consultant meeting.</p>\n<p>- Liaises with subcontractor and project manager to ensure a smoothly workflow.</p>\n<p>- Schedule, monitor and supervise the progress of RC structural work on site.</p>\n<p>- Assist in planning , controlling and co-ordinating of Architectural works.</p>\n<p>- Prepare As-built drawings.</p>\n<p>- Assist project manager in all RC structural related to site work.</p>\n<p><u>Requirement:</u></p>\n<p>- Degree/ Diploma in Civil Engineering or Building.</p>\n<p>- Familiar with coonstruction site activities.</p>\n<p>- Knowledge the schedule for FSB application, R.I inspection, TOP application , CSC and final completition certification.</p>",
